adise_6354f7ab-58ae-4d59-85b0-8cfcb26a2f4a_thumbnail_1920x1080.jpg" guid="plex://movie/69a6d4d04eebde9899593728" key="/library/metadata/69a6d4d04eebde9899593728" ratingKey="69a6d4d04eebde9899593728" summary="The North Shore is a 7 Mile stretch of paradise like no other on Earth. Every year thousands of people flock to the North Shore of Oahu to see the world&apos;s best surfers ride arguably the world&apos;s best waves. Pro surfers have created their careers, made their livings and even become legends from surfing these shores. Pro surfer Anastasia Ashley will be your tour guide and take you to the places she loves, the places she went as a kid growing up there, and introduce you to the people that always made it feel like home. We will experience and understand why she loves the North Shore, and considers it &apos;7 Miles of Paradise&apos;" type="movie" contentRating="TV-PG" duration="6201000" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://d1ki4kvnknm0kh.cloudfront.net/surfer/d524e774-34f9-4a23-b6ed-6077607149e6_7MilesOfParadise_36637fec-f14f-4d61-b98b-97508ee2fd04_poster.jpg" title="7 Miles of Paradise" userState="0"><Image alt="7 Miles of Paradise" type="coverArt" url="https://d1ki4kvnknm0kh.cloudfront.net/surfer/d524e774-34f9-4a23-b6ed-6077607149e6_7-miles-of-paradise_6354f7ab-58ae-4d59-85b0-8cfcb26a2f4a_thumbnail_1920x1080.jpg"/><Image alt="7 Miles of Paradise" type="coverPoster" url="https://d1ki4kvnknm0kh.cloudfront.net/surfer/d524e774-34f9-4a23-b6ed-6077607149e6_7MilesOfParadise_36637fec-f14f-4d61-b98b-97508ee2fd04_poster.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" id="620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" ratingKey="genre_620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" slug="sports" tag="Sports" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1773563739" duration="6201000" endsAt="1773569940" id="69ad6c5eeb4b851b62b376ce" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video></MediaContainer>
